{"tid":770134,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔係毒撚 我只係一個廢物","createTime":"2018-08-06T20:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T21:42:20.000Z","uid":136414,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1963f824c540ff9945de114680cb3c3a7756f01","tid":770134,"uid":136414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T20:08:59.000Z","msg":"我係一個長期摺係屋企既柒頭<br />\n笨手笨腳 唔識講野 內向 容易緊張<br />\n因為我成日做（有意或無意）戅鳩嘢 所以朋友成日都恥笑 抽我水<br />\n其實大多數時間我都唔介意 因為呢個係我係圈子製造話題既方法<br />\n但係有陣時其實真係會hurt 到自尊<br />\n令到我更加自卑<br />\n身邊既人 唔係完美 但係對自我既肯定一定高好多<br />\n其實一件咁脆弱 冇自信 唔識社交既廢物<br />\n到底點樣生存落去"},{"pid":"b8113607b761c61e20b052c318a35d3d9dbe74c9","tid":770134,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T20:33:28.000Z","msg":"don&rsquo;t worry be happy"},{"pid":"80291906b4e19df2f668651249256913c7b37874","tid":770134,"uid":156940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T21:05:11.000Z","msg":"死咗佢算啦"},{"pid":"6eccb3a0683e35bb950fb9912be6ad2140dbec9d","tid":770134,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T21:22:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"670b6dab5ebd7738fc6af95e08b2e6ff3d6e4ae0","tid":770134,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T21:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0ca72bfb45f1467495c6f4397a098a89abfd661","tid":770134,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T21:42:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}